'''Caroline''' works at Office Hub with [[Melissa (Don't Let's Start)|Melissa]].

==History==
When her co-worker, Melissa, was carjacked and had to be taken to the hospital, Caroline, along with two other co-workers, [[Keith (Don't Let's Start)|Keith]] and [[Jacki]], accompanied her to the hospital. When asked by the doctors for information, they had to admit that they don't know Melissa well. Despite this, they waited of her at the hospital and came to her room to see her after she had surgery.

==Relationships==
===Friendships===
She seems to get along well with her co-workers Keith, Jacki, and Melissa. When Melissa was hospitalized, the others visited her together.

==Career==
She repairs computers at Office Hub.
